<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Défi terminé !</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 30px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 30px;
            padding: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            color: #764ba2;
            font-size: 36px;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .emoji {
            font-size: 60px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .content {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa 0%, #e9ecef 100%);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .defi-titre {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #667eea;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .stats {
            display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between; /* mieux que space-around */
    gap: 20px; /* espace entre les blocs */
    margin: 20px 0;
    padding: 20px;
    background: white;
    border-radius: 15px;
        }
        .stat-item {
            text-align: center;
    flex: 1;
        }
        .stat-value {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #764ba2;
        }
        .stat-label {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.3);
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            color: #999;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="emoji">🏆</div>
            <h1>FÉLICITATIONS !</h1>
            <p style="color: #666; font-size: 18px;">Tu as relevé un nouveau défi !</p>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <p style="font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px;">Bravo <strong>{{ user.firstName }}</strong> !</p>
            
            <div class="defi-titre">{{ defi.titre }}</div>
            
            <p style="color: #666; margin: 20px 0;">{{ defi.description }}</p>

            <div class="stats">
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <div class="stat-value">{{ progression|round }}/{{ objectif }}</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">{{ unite }}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <div class="stat-value">{{ defi.difficulte }}/5</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Difficulté</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <div class="stat-value">{{ date_fin|date('d/m/Y') }}</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Terminé le</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <p style="text-align: center;">
                <em>"Chaque défi relevé est une victoire sur soi-même"</em>
            </p>

            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="{{ app_url }}{{ path('app_front_defi_show', {'id': defi.id}) }}" class="button">
                    Voir mon défi
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>LibraryHub - Ta bibliothèque intelligente</p>
            <p style="font-size: 12px;">© {{ annee }} LibraryHub. Tous droits réservés.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>